column2: SELECT    s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, zp.z, el.ra1, el.dec1 into mydb.MyTable_# from mydb.BCG2 as el   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq( el.ra1, el.dec1, #) AS near    JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON near.specObjID=s.specObjID   JOIN Photoz as zp ON zp.objID = s.specObjID   WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=#
